desc: Dry Ice Energy Ireland (DIEI) is a dry ice pellet wholesaler and the official distributor in Ireland and United kingdom of the Champ Turbo dry ice energy blasting machine. Dry Ice Energy Ireland is the first operator in Ireland to produce and sell 1.7mm dry ice pellets to industry and retail marketsectors.

layout.text: The plug-and-play dry ice cleaning! Compressed air on - dry ice in - and off you go!
